window.bookSummaryJSON = "Imagine the possibilities if we discovered the power to change our lives, and our world, within the cells of our own bodies! <br>On this remarkable audio program, you will: <br> <li> Discover that the ancient message, and the name of God, are encoded into the cells of your body and all life</li> <li> Learn and understand the lost key that allows DNA to be translated into language and words</li> <li> Cross the traditional boundaries of science and spirituality to discover how the message in your DNA holds the power to heal your body, resolve conflict, and create peace between families and nations </li> <li> See how to switch the healing codes of your body to \"ON\"! </li>"; 
